  }, "v2"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF3 m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi r\u1EA5t gi\xE0u \u1EDF Ma-\xF4n nh\u01B0ng c\xF3 \u0111\u1EA5t \u0111ai \u1EDF C\u1EA1t-m\xEAn. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF3 ba ng\xE0n chi\xEAn v\xE0 m\u1ED9t ng\xE0n d\xEA. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111ang h\u1EDBt l\xF4ng chi\xEAn \u1EDF C\u1EA1t-m\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v3"
  }, "v3"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi t\xEAn l\xE0 Na-banh thu\u1ED9c d\xF2ng d\xF5i Ca-l\xE9p. V\u1EE3 t\xEAn l\xE0 A-bi-ga-in. N\xE0ng r\u1EA5t xinh \u0111\u1EB9p v\xE0 kh\xF4n ngoan, nh\u01B0ng Na-banh th\xEC hung \xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v4"
  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi \u0110a-v\xEDt \u0111ang \u1EDF trong sa m\u1EA1c th\xEC nghe Na-banh \u0111ang h\u1EDBt l\xF4ng chi\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v5"
  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "N\xEAn \xF4ng sai n\u0103m thanh ni\xEAn b\u1EA3o, \"H\xE3y \u0111i xu\u1ED1ng g\u1EB7p Na-banh \u1EDF C\u1EA1t-m\xEAn, nh\xE2n danh ta ch\xE0o th\u0103m ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v6"
  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "v\xE0 n\xF3i, 'Ch\xFAc \xF4ng v\xE0 gia \u0111\xECnh c\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng ai thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 \xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c m\u1EA1nh kho\u1EBB. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v7"
  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "T\xF4i nghe \xF4ng \u0111ang h\u1EDBt l\xF4ng chi\xEAn. Khi c\xE1c k\u1EBB ch\u0103n chi\xEAn c\u1EE7a \xF4ng \u1EDF v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng t\xF4i, ch\xFAng t\xF4i kh\xF4ng l\xE0m g\xEC h\u1EA1i h\u1ECD c\u1EA3. Trong su\u1ED1t th\u1EDDi gian c\xE1c k\u1EBB ch\u0103n chi\xEAn \xF4ng \u1EDF C\u1EA1t-m\xEAn, h\u1ECD kh\xF4ng b\u1ECB m\u1EA5t v\u1EADt g\xEC. "), mdx("h6", {
