  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "\xD4ng h\xE3y h\u1ECFi h\u1ECD, h\u1ECD s\u1EBD cho \xF4ng bi\u1EBFt. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i \u0111\u1EBFn v\u1EDBi \xF4ng khi h\u1ECD \u0111ang vui v\u1EBB cho n\xEAn xin \xF4ng h\xE3y nh\xE2n t\u1EEB \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi c\xE1c b\u1EA1n tr\u1EBB c\u1EE7a t\xF4i. Xin \xF4ng c\u1EA5p cho h\u1ECD v\xE0 cho b\u1EA1n \xF4ng l\xE0 \u0110a-v\xEDt nh\u1EEFng g\xEC \xF4ng c\xF3 s\u1EB5n.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
